    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>As often, <strong>guava</strong> has what you need. </p>\n\n<p>To go from byte array to int: <code>Ints.fromBytesArray</code>, doc <a href=\"https://guava.dev/releases/19.0/api/docs/com/google/common/primitives/Ints.html#fromByteArray(byte[])\" rel=\"noreferrer\">here</a> </p>\n\n<p>To go from int to byte array: <code>Ints.toByteArray</code>, doc <a href=\"https://guava.dev/releases/19.0/api/docs/com/google/common/primitives/Ints.html#toByteArray(int)\" rel=\"noreferrer\">here</a> </p>\n"
  }, {
